108
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:55,560
“It is likely to lead to years of legal
wrangling.”

109
00:04:55,560 --> 00:05:00,070
Man, I can see why everyone just ignores the
WTO.

110
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:03,190
And why President Trump thinks it’s the
worst deal ever.

111
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,510
No, seriously.

112
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:09,620
“I would say the WTO is the single worst
trade deal ever made,

113
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:10,750
