114
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:13,400
I would withdraw from the WTO.”

115
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:16,110
The world of Chinese business is incredibly
murky,

116
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:18,730
especially because of the close working relationship

117
00:05:18,730 --> 00:05:22,470
private businesses have to have with the Chinese
government.

118
00:05:22,470 --> 00:05:25,300
