126
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:52,150
“In China, businessmen who fly too high
have a habit

127
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:55,770
of falling out of favor with the ruling Communist
Party.”

128
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:59,400
But Jack Ma says not to worry, there are no
charges against him,

129
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,400
