132
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:11,800
As he put it, he’d rather die on the beach
than in his office.

133
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,390
Die on the beach?

134
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,730
In China?

135
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:19,090
Um...dying in the office doesn’t actually
sound so bad.

136
00:06:19,090 --> 00:06:22,140
Anyway, speaking of having a chance to live
life,

137
00:06:22,140 --> 00:06:26,040
three offices related to family planning have
closed down.

138
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:29,000
“Family Planning” in China is a euphemism

139
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,530
that refers to the Communist Party-run offices

140
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:34,920
